<p><b>David Fairclough</b> (born <a href="Liverpool" title="Liverpool">Liverpool</a>, 5 January 1957) is a retired <a href="England" title="England">English</a> footballer, most famous for playing for <a href="Liverpool_F.C." title="Liverpool F.C.">Liverpool</a> as a striker during the 1970s and 1980s.</p>
